I didn&#39;t intend for either to be ominous.  I just think we don&#39;t know who 
we&#39;re really comunicating with through the boxes.  It could be space 
aliens for all we know. They definitely don&#39;t sound like the EVP&#39;s I&#39;ve 
gotten in haunted places. They are in a class by themselves. Maybe we&#39;ll 
know for sure some day.

As for the loved ones, I personally think they hang around for the 
funeral, then they&#39;re off into a new baby body as fast as they can go. The 
ones who hang around and become ghosts are probably in the less than 1% 
category of people who do that. The rest are growing up with new parents 
somewhere and getting to believe in Santa Claus (or whatever) again.
:-)

Zack

